KATERINI chased off the inside then angled to the rail, got boxed in from the three-eighths to the five-sixteenths pole, remained inside to the stretch, altered out at the eighth pole and finished gamely for the show. BACK ON THE STREET bobbled a bit leaving the gate, chased three deep at the back into the turn, moved out to the four path around the bend, failed to find the needed rally in the lane but got up for a minor award. DOLLY MAY (IRE) saved ground from off the pace and failed to threaten. TRAVEL SMART got crowded between rivals early, raced two wide at the back into the turn, ran up behind a rival near the quarter pole and had to shifted three wide leaving the bend, churned on down the lane but failed to menace. JAMIES INHERITANCE broke out a bit at the start, tracked outside rivals then raced outside a rival in the two path into the turn, remained two wide into the stretch and weakened. CHEERFUL CHARM forwardly placed off the rail into the turn, dropped back three then four wide on the bend and had little left for the drive.
